Pao De Acucar’s Diniz Seeks New Investors for Merger, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-13T01:43:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/pao-de-acucar-s-diniz-seeks-new-investors-for-merger-ft-says.html
Advisers to Cia. Brasileira de
Distribuicao Grupo Pao de Acucar Chairman Abilio Diniz are
seeking new investors to replace Brazil’s national development
bank, BNDES, which said it would be reducing its stake in the
proposed merger between Pao de Acucar and  Carrefour SA (CA) ’s Brazil
unit, the Financial Times reported, citing a person close to the
negotiations.  To contact the reporter on this story:
